{"tid":1565353,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"要跳閘就全世界同一時間一齊跳！","createTime":"2019-09-13T06:12:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T06:13:46.000Z","uid":177270,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8281118d54e09ebc6b25489f3a68a282dc609c21","tid":1565353,"uid":177270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:12:42.000Z","msg":"而家黨鐵用加價嘅錢請撚咗咁撚多捉飛狗幫佢睇住每一道閘，一個人跳閘基本上係捉硬，好難怪咁多人唔跳<br />\n<br />\n最簡單嘅解決方法就係大家返工放工嗰陣<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">約一個時間全世界一齊跳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n例如朝早返工7:00, 7:15, 7:30, 7:45 etc<br />\n夜晚放工就18:00, 18:15 如此類推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每次每個閘口50人一齊跳，佢每個閘口放10隻捉飛狗都捉唔倒幾多個</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">仲要捉完第一轉都未處理完，下一轉嘅人已經跳緊！</span>，佢哋絕對冇咁多人手處理<br />\n<br />\n除非佢叫埋啲防暴狗每日一齊捉飛，如果唔係全世界一齊跳黨鐵一定冇我哋辦法"},{"pid":"08c29a734a78e6113e51cb8ae31eb20f4fe11598","tid":1565353,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:13:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"}]}